Steps in this tutorial:

x	1. Incorporate Bootstrap for some simple style
x	2. Add Emberjs
x	3. Create simple startup page and playing field
x	4. Rewrite app in coffeescript
x   5. Add client-side tests in jasmine
x   6. Add server tests in jasmine
x	7. Add session state implemented with Redis
x	8. Add game state storage in CouchDB
x	9. Implement rink rendering
x	10. Implement (non-colliding) player position computation
x	11. Update game state when requested at /gs/:id
x	12. Implement player and puck wall collision
x   13. Set acceleration from mouse event
	14. Implement collision between player and puck
	15. Update players via websockets


